metadata.name: Venus Diamond
metadata.description:
The second planet from the “Navaratna” collection is Venus with its corresponding gem - Diamond.

Her alluring image – the brightest planet in the sky - has always attracted the attention of people.  
This planet is a symbol of the most powerful force in the Universe - the creative energy of Love.

Venus is considered to be a particularly benevolent planet, as it rules human feelings, pleasures, joy and beauty.  
She has always been favorable to people whose hearts are full of love, both platonic and passionate.

Venus has assumed the form of a beautiful female, floating among bright celestial bodies.  
Her aura glows with a soft pink light in the darkness of space.

Detached and strong, yet captivating and gentle, the image of Venus is imprinted in the mind.  
She hypnotizes the viewer and is impossible to forget.
